title: SUPERSIZED EPISODE! RHONJ/RHOC/Bennifer/Kardashians & Keltie Knight (Ladygang)!
itunes:title: SUPERSIZED EPISODE! RHONJ/RHOC/Bennifer/Kardashians & Keltie Knight (Ladygang)!
description:
Danny recaps this week's captivating episode of The Real Housewives of New Jersey, which saw the women in Nashville in the midst of chaos! The Real Housewives of Orange County had their finale, PLUS Keltie Knight from Ladygang joins Danny at the end to discuss Britney's pregnancy, Bennifer's engagement, and Kardashians moving to Hulu in this super-sized episode of Everything Iconic!


Keltie Knight: 45:00ish
